{"tid":1631652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 各位五毛，你係咪以為我哋會驚你？","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:15.000Z","uid":162711,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"89ce6567c69a6d05d81f4dceb1a67431078ccf1d","tid":1631652,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"五毛具備以下特徵，各位手足見到呢啲人麻煩<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無視</span></span></strong>佢哋<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚幫佢哋推post</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n五毛特徵: <br />\n<br />\n1. 帶風向<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">鼓吹人亂尻咁裝修/獅鳥/搞人地宗教/作出一切無理嘅激進行為</span></span>，利用勇武手足憤怒嘅情緒同埋勇氣，目的就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將和勇分化</span></span>，企圖抹黑勇武，嚇鳩啲淺黃同中立派<br />\n<br />\n有啲就企圖鼓吹叫人打陣地戰，呢啲真係要小心，因為個後果就係俾狗拉，返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n2.係又屌唔係又屌，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最鍾意就係屌鳩啲和理非</strong></span></span> 又話和理非民意撚，我梗係唔係care班藍屍，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>而係care中立派/淺黃淺藍/一班爹哋媽咪銀髮族</strong></span></span>。或者屌鳩啲遊行集中撚，唔排除鼓吹集中撚嗰班有一部份係鬼，但係都有好大部份人唔係，係咁屌都冇意思㗎啦，只可以話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">做法不完美，可接受，需要改善</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n但呢班友係又屌唔係又屌，其實就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>想撩交嗌，分化連登手足</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n3.做乜柒都話核爆都唔割<br />\n<br />\n班風向撚就係想利用我哋當初嘅宗旨: 不割蓆，不薦灰，不分化，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">企圖合理化一切走火入魔嘅行為</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你真係手足，我相信你會好樂意聆聽我哋嘅意見，唔會堅持帶風向/堅持激進落去。即使我哋係和理非，冇勇氣打狗，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>至少我哋時刻保持警覺同理智 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n但如果你係風向撚，你已經好有可能係鬼，fact check 咗之後，Sorry 我地要割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布: 有以上特徵嘅，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">一律有可能係鬼</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n如有遺漏，請各位手足喺下面補充<br />\n<br />\n香港人要團結啊，不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時刻警覺五毛嘅出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada2b277381daa943c2df0f7b7f025f41a329e56","tid":1631652,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:59.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f305940e5d6f9ba3ec30bf8ba166b20acf2f8a5e","tid":1631652,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ceb7aebcc6733e165d39ddb5893aa9cca5feaae","tid":1631652,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1a1296ab1138272ff5af459bf5af7ff1520880f","tid":1631652,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6c59940393b3a4f28196251120093001a8c5e07","tid":1631652,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"人人做文宣"},{"pid":"a25f114ef904d64b910abc9b0cb9ebde1d634f82","tid":1631652,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"呢到呢幾日係勁多五毛搞分化 建議手足暫時唔好上連登住 冷靜下先講真 去twitter做文宣好過喺呢到睇post留言<br />\n<br />\n利申: 勇武和理非永不割蓆 齊上齊落"},{"pid":"b